OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1772012417
OL,3,CFormer detective 'inundated' teenage
OL,4,Cgirl, 14, with inappropriate messages
OL,6,FA former detective who "inundated" a
OL,7,Fvulnerable 14-year-old girl with
OL,8,Finappropriate messages has been
OL,9,Fconvicted of misconduct in public
OL,10,Foffice.
OL,12,FJohn Hamilton, who was a Northumbria
OL,13,FPolice detective constable, was found
OL,14,Fguilty by jurors at Teesside Crown
OL,15,FCourt following an investigation by
OL,16,Fthe Independent Office for Police
OL,17,FConduct (IOPC).
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1772012417
OL,3,CFormer detective 'inundated' teenage
OL,4,Cgirl, 14, with inappropriate messages
OL,6,FHamilton, who worked within the
OL,7,Fforce's child and adult protection
OL,8,Fsafeguarding department, had denied
OL,9,Fthe charge during an earlier hearing
OL,10,Fat North Tyneside Magistrates' Court
OL,11,Fin August 2024.
OL,13,FThe IOPC began a criminal
OL,14,Finvestigation in November 2021
OL,15,Ffollowing a referral from Northumbria
OL,16,FPolice.
OL,18,FHamilton was suspended but retired
OL,19,Fwhile the investigation was underway.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1772012417
OL,3,CFormer detective 'inundated' teenage
OL,4,Cgirl, 14, with inappropriate messages
OL,6,FIt was found that Hamilton had been
OL,7,Fassigned to an investigation involving
OL,8,Fa 14-year-old girl who had been a
OL,9,Fvictim of a serious sexual assault.
OL,11,FOn 23 September 2021, Northumbria
OL,12,FPolice received a referral from the
OL,13,Fschool that raised concerns about the
OL,14,Fcontact the detective had with the
OL,15,Fgirl.
OL,17,FShe reported to school staff that he
OL,18,Fhad been contacting her excessively
OL,19,Fvia text messages and felt she was
OL,20,Fbeing inundated with messages from
OL,21,Fhim, the IOPC said.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1772012417
OL,3,CFormer detective 'inundated' teenage
OL,4,Cgirl, 14, with inappropriate messages
OL,6,FHamilton spoke to the girl at school
OL,7,Fon three occasions and had told staff
OL,8,Fto leave the room while he was with
OL,9,Fher on one visit.
OL,11,FThe girl reported that the officer had
OL,12,Fmade little mention of the matters he
OL,13,Fhad been assigned to investigate. The
OL,14,Fofficer made two further unannounced
OL,15,Fvisits to the school and had asked the
OL,16,Fgirl in a message whether he could
OL,17,Ftake her out on a drive and return her
OL,18,Fhome afterwards.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1772012417
OL,3,CFormer detective 'inundated' teenage
OL,4,Cgirl, 14, with inappropriate messages
OL,6,FAnalysis of the officer's work phone
OL,7,Funcovered 268 text messages exchanged
OL,8,Fbetween Hamilton and the girl on eight
OL,9,Fseparate days between 10-23 September,
OL,10,F2021, with many sent late at night or
OL,11,Fin the early hours of the morning.
OL,13,FAn IOPC spokesman said: "We found
OL,14,Fevidence of the officer sending three
OL,15,Flate-night voice messages on one
OL,16,Fevening in the two-week period with
OL,17,Fthe officer's voice slurred throughout.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1772012417
OL,3,CFormer detective 'inundated' teenage
OL,4,Cgirl, 14, with inappropriate messages
OL,6,F"Evidence gathered also showed a lack
OL,7,Fof records in respect of the contact
OL,8,Fhe had with the girl despite the fact
OL,9,FDC Hamilton was duty bound to do so."
OL,11,FIOPC Director Emily Barry said: "DC
OL,12,FHamilton was an experienced police
OL,13,Fofficer with over 24 years of service
OL,14,Fso he knew perfectly well the
OL,15,Fstandards of professional behaviour
OL,16,Fexpected of him, whether on or off
OL,17,Fduty.
OL,26,@sD@aOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1772012417
OL,3,CFormer detective 'inundated' teenage
OL,4,Cgirl, 14, with inappropriate messages
OL,6,F"The seriousness of his actions were
OL,7,Fexacerbated by the fact he worked in a
OL,8,Fsafeguarding team and was meant to be
OL,9,Fprotecting a 14-year-old girl who was
OL,10,Fin an extremely vulnerable position as
OL,11,Fa victim of crime.
OL,13,F"Police officers are made fully aware
OL,14,Ffrom the outset of their
OL,15,Fresponsibilities with how they deal
OL,16,Fwith members of the public they meet
OL,17,Fthrough their professional duties.
OL,18,FHamilton completely abused his
OL,19,Fposition of trust and has rightfully
OL,20,Fbeen held accountable for his actions.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1772012417
OL,3,CFormer detective 'inundated' teenage
OL,4,Cgirl, 14, with inappropriate messages
OL,6,F"We are always incredibly grateful to
OL,7,Fthe brave people who speak out about
OL,8,Fthe inappropriate behaviour they have
OL,9,Fexperienced or witnessed. We want
OL,10,Fpeople to feel empowered to speak up
OL,11,Fif they believe an officer has acted
OL,12,Finappropriately. You are not alone;
OL,13,Fyou will be listened to; and your
OL,14,Fexperiences will be taken seriously."
OL,16,FThe IOPC concluded its investigation
OL,17,Fin February 2023 and referred a file
OL,18,Fof evidence to the Crown Prosecution
OL,19,FService (CPS). Hamilton was charged in
OL,20,FAugust 2024.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1772012417
OL,3,CFormer detective 'inundated' teenage
OL,4,Cgirl, 14, with inappropriate messages
OL,6,FThe IOPC also determined that the
OL,7,Fformer officer should face a gross
OL,8,Fmisconduct hearing in relation to his
OL,9,Fconduct. The watchdog is now liaising
OL,10,Fwith Northumbria Police about
OL,11,Fdisciplinary proceedings.
OL,13,FDet Supt Donna Rose, from Northumbria
OL,14,FPolice's Professional Standards
OL,15,FDepartment, said: "Firstly, we want to
OL,16,Frecognise the bravery of the victim in
OL,17,Fthis case in coming forward. When
OL,18,Fconcerns were raised in relation to
OL,19,Fthis individual he was suspended from
OL,20,Fduty.
OL,26,@wD@SOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1772012417
OL,3,CFormer detective 'inundated' teenage
OL,4,Cgirl, 14, with inappropriate messages
OL,6,F"The case was referred to the
OL,7,FIndependent Office for Police Conduct
OL,8,F(IOPC) who conducted an investigation,
OL,9,Fduring the course of which he retired.
OL,10,FHis actions were completely
OL,11,Funacceptable and are in no way
OL,12,Frepresentative of the overwhelming
OL,13,Fmajority of officers, staff and
OL,14,Fvolunteers at Northumbria Police who
OL,15,Fcome to work to make a positive
OL,16,Fdifference to people's lives.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,423,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F422A1772012417
OL,3,CFormer detective 'inundated' teenage
OL,4,Cgirl, 14, with inappropriate messages
OL,6,F"As a force, we have made it very
OL,7,Fclear that when someone falls below
OL,8,Fthe standards expected and which they
OL,9,Fmade a commitment to uphold we will
OL,10,Ftake appropriate action. We can
OL,11,Fconfirm following his conviction
OL,12,Fmisconduct proceedings are also being
OL,13,Fprogressed."
OL,15,FHamilton will be sentenced on 10 April.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G11/11
